  m_text: "<b>\u0398</b> \u2014 <color=#FFA500>Total Internal Angle Sum</color>\n<i>Sum
    of the three echo arcs (\u0398 = \u03A3 \u03C6\u1D62)</i>\n<color=#AAAAAA>Perfect
    triadic closure occurs at \u0398 = 2\u03C0 radians.</color>\n<color=#00FFFF>Deviation
    from 2\u03C0 introduces curvature, charge, and identity tension.</color>"
